	(text "Delay element to convert 33% duty cycle to 50% duty cycle\nwell I think like 47.5% duty cycle with a phase shift\nrelative to core clock of 29°. But I honestly don't know\nhow relevant this is to the function of this computer."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 105.156 210.312 0)
